<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">10.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The role of culture in health assessment, data collection methods, physical examination skills, evaluation of systems (skin and attachments, muscle and skeleton, cardio-vascular, respiratory, gastrointestinal, excretory, neurological system). Features and health risks of the individual according to age</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413944&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
