<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">13.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to psychology and history of psychology, Research methods and psychological tests in psychology, Neurobiological basis of psychology and sensation perception, Cognitive psychology, Learning and intelligence, Consciousness, sleep and psychoactive substances, Developmental psychology, Social psychology, Personality psychology, Emotions, stress, related psychological processes and health psychology, Psychological disorders-adult, Psychological disorders-child&amp;adolescent, Communication</Data></Cell>
