<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HSEC 228</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Sexual and Reproductive Health</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">• Opening and introduction, aims and objectives of the course,
• Students&apos; expectations from theoretical education
• Expressing Sexuality-Reproductive Health and Sexual Health in the World and in Turkey
• Sexual Action Physiology
• Sexual Myths
• Societies&apos; Perspective on Sexuality
• Sexual and Reproductive Health by Age Periods-Childhood and Adolescent Period
• Sexual and Reproductive Health by Age Periods- Pregnancy-Menopause-Old Age
• Sexual Dysfunctions
• Evaluation of Sexual Function-Sexual History
• Safe Sex-STD
• Sexual Violence and Approach to Victims
• Family Planning
• Conditions Affecting Sexual Function
• Sexual Dysfunctions in Infertile Couples</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413756&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HSEC 230</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Palliative Care</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Purpose, definition and principles of palliative care, current status of palliative care and palliative care nursing in our country.
Pain management
respiratory system symptoms
management (Dyspnea-Cough-Hemoptysis)
Nutrition, Anorexia and Cachexia Management in Palliative Care
Nausea and vomiting management
Diarrhea and constipation management
Insomnia and fatigue management
Communication with the patient and his family, the patient&apos;s psychosocial problems
Caring for the dying patient, good death / peaceful death concept
Loss / grief and support
Ethical and legal aspects of palliative care
COURSE ASSESSMENT</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413933&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HSEC 232</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Home Care</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">It includes related knowledge and skills to the status and history of Home Care Services in Turkey and in the world, the role and responsibilities of Home Care Services team, planning, implementation and evaluation of the maintenance of individuals who need home care</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413855&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
