<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HSEC 238</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Patient and Employee Safety</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">* Introduction to Patient and Employee Safety course * Basic Concepts in Patient and Employee Safety
* Safety Culture
Patient and Employee Safety in the Documentation Process
* Drug Safety
* Transfusion Safety
*Patient and Employee Safety in the Operating Room
* Patient and Employee Safety in the Intensive Care Unit
Sexually Transmitted Diseases Seminar
* Infection Control in Patient and Employee Safety
* Legal View and Responsibilities in Patient and Employee Safety
* Communication in Patient and Employee Safety
*Prevention of Errors with SBAR Technique
* Employee Health and Safety
*Student presentations
* Student Presentations</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413856&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HSEC 240</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Children and Communication</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Being aware of the child&apos;s profile, healthy communication with children according to age groups, non-verbal communication with children and listening to children, activities related to child communication, problem solving skills in children, emotional neglect and abuse of children, communication with children with special needs, communication with children in hospital, therapeutic game</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413758&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
