<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">10.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Leadership process, leadership styles, role of leadership in nursing practices, nurse leadership in the development of health policies, leadership and power relationship, power of vision, professional and individual positioning.</Data></Cell>
