<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Structure, function, healing and bone metabolism of the basic anatomical formations in the musculoskeletal system, Examination and evaluation of the musculoskeletal system, Osteosynthesis and Biomaterials, Pediatric Orthopedic Diseases and Care, Geriatric Orthopedic Diseases and Care, Orthopedic Emergencies and Care Principles in Musculoskeletal Trauma, Fractures and Farktür Liaison Nursing, Care in Total Joint Replacement Surgery, Complication Management in Orthopedic Surgery, Orthopedics and ERAS Protocols, Safe Lifting and Carrying Techniques for Orthopedic Patients.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413829&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
