<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Subjects related to drug administration to patients based on eight right principles, Prevention of Medication Defects, and corticosteroid drugs, drugs for coagulation disorders, cardiovascular system drugs, respiratory system drugs, female and male health drugs and pediatric drug applications are discussed.</Data></Cell>
