<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">It contributes to the use of this in nursing practice by understanding the importance of culture and intercultural nursing while providing nursing care to the individual, family and society.</Data></Cell>
