<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course includes the characteristics of behavior in communication, the use of I Language and addressing language and their effects on communication, the importance and benefits of assertiveness in personal and professional life, the acquisition of assertiveness and change of behaviour.</Data></Cell>
