<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to Rehabilitation Nursing Course
General Concepts and Principles of Rehabilitation Nursing
Self-Care in Rehabilitation Patients: Bowel and Bladder Management
Self-Care in Rehabilitation Patients: Swallowing and Nutritional Status
Self-Care in Rehabilitation Patients: Education of Patients and Families
Rehabilitation in Special Situations: Cardiac and Pulmonary Rehabilitation
Rehabilitation in special situations: traumatic brain injury, Spinal Cord injury
Rehabilitation in special situations: Rehabilitation in individuals with amputation
Evaluation
Rehabilitation in Special Situations: Psychiatric Rehabilitation
Gerontological Rehabilitation
Musculoskeletal Injuries in Rehabilitation Nursing
Pediatric Rehabilitation
Student Group Presentations</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413937&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
