<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Social Awareness Project</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">07.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">It includes voluntary social sensitivity project, planning, implementation principles, evaluation Principles, Project reporting topics.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413803&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HEM 432</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">English for Specific Purposes II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">A2+/B1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413752&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HEM 452</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Public Health Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">By enabling the training of well-equipped and conscious public health nurses, it provides to gain knowledge, attitude and skills in order to protect and improve the health of individuals living in the community.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413953&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HEM 454</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Management in Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Hemşirelikte yönetim dersi, mesleki alanda yasal ve idari sorumlukların kavranmasına, meslek üyelerinin çalışacakları sağlık bakım hizmeti veren birimlerde ve örgütlerde yönetim ve organizasyon ile ilgili süreçlerde rol ve sorumluluk almalarına katkı sağlar</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413906&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HEM 456</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Surgical Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Cerrahi tedavinin uygulandığı sağlık bakım alanlarında cerrahi süreç içerisindeki bireyin fizyolojik, psikolojik ve sosyal gereksinimlerini değerlendirmesi, etkin ve güvenli bakım uygulamalarına yönelik bilgi ve beceri geliştirilmesine katkı sağlar</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413835&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HEM 458</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Women&apos;s Health and Diseases Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Bu dersi alan bir mezun, gebelik dönemi olağan sorunlarını ve riskli gebelikleri ayırt edebilir, normal doğum eyleminde hemşirelik desteği sağlar, uygun doğum sonu bakımı verebilir ve Üreme organlarının iyi ve kötü huylu tümörlerine yönelik hemşirelik girişimlerini planlar, uygular ve hasta sonuçlarını değerlendirir</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413836&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HEM 460</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Mental Health and Disease Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Fiziksel sağlık sorunu olan hasta ve hasta yakınlarının ruh sağlığının korunması, geliştirilmesi ve ruh sağlığının bozulduğu durumlarda bakım, tedavi ve rehabilitasyonda hemşirelik bilgi ve becerilerinin kazanılmasına katkı sağlar.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413876&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HEM 462</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Educational Principles and Methods in Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Öğrencinin; hasta ve yakınlarının eğitimi konusunda sahip olduğu kuramsal bilgi, tutum ve becerileri klinikte uygulamaya yansıtması ve yetkinlik kazanması; kurumda/kurum tarafından planlanan sağlık eğitimi faaliyetlerini görmesi ve dahil olması; hizmet içi eğitim konusunda kurumda planlanan oryantasyon ve hizmet içi eğitim faaliyetlerini gözlemlemesi konularında katkı sağlar</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413821&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HEM 464</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Internal Medicine Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Bu dersi alan bir mezun, küresel acil durum olanD iyabetes Mellitus ve yönetimini, ülkemizde ve dünyada prevalansı artan kardiyovasküler hastalıklar ve kanserlerde tedavi, bakım ve semptom yönetimini, farklı hastalıklarda palyatif bakımı, inme, göğüs ağrısı ve diğer acil durumlarda hastaların kritik bakımını planlar, uygular ve hasta sonuçlarını değerlendirir</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413822&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">HEM 466</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Child Health and Disease Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+20+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">11</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">25.06.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Çocuk ve ailesinin sağlığını koruma ve geliştirme, riskli/hasta çocuğu tanılama, bakım verme ve değerlendirme konusunda bilgi, tutum ve becerilerin gelişimine katkıda bulunur</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413875&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
</Table>
