<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 175</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Creativity and Art</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Recognize the concept of creativity. Classify the branches of art. Learn the method of drama. Develop creative thinking skills. Use creative techniques. Apply creative and artistic activities in social and professional life. Evaluate the obstacles in front of creativity.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413807&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 176</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Music, Individual and Society</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Müzikal kavramları tanır. Müzik tarihi dönemlerini öğrenir. Müzik, birey ve toplum ilişkisini kavrar. Müziğe sosyolojik bakış açısı geliştirir. Sosyal yaşamda temel müzik bilgisini kullanır. Müzik, birey ve toplum ilişkisini değerlendirir. Bir sanat dalı olan müzik üzerine interdisipliner yaklaşımla tartışır.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413806&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 178</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Modern Scientific Research Methods</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">To be able to understand the basic principles and processes in the realization of research, To learn different research methods, To be able to analyze data and develop solutions, and to interpret the results obtained with the help of software.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413805&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
