<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 221</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History of the Horror Film</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">By the end of the course, the students will have a thorough grasp of the history of the horror film, its formal and narrative strategies, and the various critical and theoretical approaches used to examine it.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413770&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nursing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 221</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History of the Horror Film</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The students will also expand their knowledge of the complex relationship of horror cinema to issues of identity, nation, ideology, and affect.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413770&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
