<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Explains the place of health technologies in specific areas (home care, diabetes, intensive care, operating room, sterilization, children, oncology, wound care).</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413952&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
